{"tid":438442,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 10 再次被踢爆收集用戶個人資料","createTime":"2017-10-17T02:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T13:49:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2078923e571c1a57ec3612257398c26e718eb41d","tid":438442,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"荷蘭資料保護局近期指出，微軟旗下作業系統Windows 10系統，未經使用者允許<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，透過微軟瀏覽器 Edge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，蒐集使用者關於app使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、網路行為等等個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並表示「微軟並未明確告知使用者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不管是蒐集數據的行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以及數據後續使用的目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，而經過對Windows 10 多版本的調查，荷蘭當局也確認微軟利用預設設定的方式，未告知使用者設定內的包含收集數據的動作之下，讓微軟得以建立使用者個人化廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-r061Vs9lWhU/WZwP_x99_qI/AAAAAAAEPcs/BkeQcgVK6IcppGpf4rp68ATYJfyRYpptACHMYCw/599c0ef842f72.jpg?imgmax=610\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-r061Vs9lWhU%2FWZwP_x99_qI%2FAAAAAAAEPcs%2FBkeQcgVK6IcppGpf4rp68ATYJfyRYpptACHMYCw%2F599c0ef842f72.jpg%3Fimgmax%3D610&h=262d7857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-10-15/100624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2017-10-15%2F100624&d=4r1OJhd6hxEzagf6THXhUI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=656714fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-10-15/100624</a></div>"},{"pid":"55fa118e35a000f39c44b316cc3ca24a45f52d4f","tid":438442,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"mac用家路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=